<item>
            <title>[LU-2057] sanity.sh test_205 failed: no job stats implemented for OFD</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2057</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Job Stats feature implemented in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-694&quot; title=&quot;Job Stats&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-694&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-694&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; was not implemented for OFD, and was missed during the orion_head_sync rebase.  This is causing sanity.sh test_205 to fail when run with USE_OFD=yes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The job stats fails with:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;mdt.testfs-MDT0000.job_stats=clear
error: set_param: /proc/{fs,sys}/{lnet,lustre}/obdfilter/*/job_stats: Found no match
 sanity test_205: @@@@@@ FAIL: No job stats found on OST ost0
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
